summary: A small shack fit for an archer, complete with an archery range and very short storyline.
descriptionHtml:
A small shack located near Whiterun, fit for an archer, complete with an archery range and very short storyline.
Find out what happened to the owner of the cabin by reading the book next to the bed.

I hope you guys like it, its simple to install just download using NMM or take the esp file and drop it into your data folder. This file has NO requirements just install and play.
Also if you liked this mod please subscribe to my youtube channel:
http://www.youtube.com/user/ThePVTAEROCK
And check out my other mod called "The Whiterun Hideout".

(Also I do know there is a problem with the weapons plaque, for some people who tested it, it works, for some it doesn't, ill figure it out ASAP)

I will add more stuff to this mod and fix bugs if needed:
Version 1.0: First release
Version 1.1: Fixed clipping issue, made the shack more fit for an Archer.
author: PVTAEROCK
